data.description: Updated three bedroom two bath located in an established neighborhood close to schools, parks, shopping and on the bus line. Kitchen cabinets and countertops updated, stove and dishwasher to be installed, new carpet in each bedroom. Both bathrooms have been updated. The homes has been painted throughout. This home is located near Sugarberry park, Cedar Ridge Preserve, Park in the Woods recreation Center.  Buyer and Buyer's Agent to confirm all information.
